snippet: An Egyptian court ruled Wednesday against the extradition to Libya of Ahmed Qaddaf al-Dam, a former close aide of Col. Muammar el-Qaddafi.
abstract: Egyptian court rules against extradition to Libya of Ahmed Qaddaf al-Dam, former close aide of ousted dictator Col Muammar el-Qaddafi.
lead_paragraph: An Egyptian court ruled Wednesday against the extradition to Libya of Ahmed Qaddaf al-Dam, a former close aide of Col. Muammar el-Qaddafi.

headline.seo: Egypt: Court Rules Against Extradition of Former Qaddafi Aide to Libya
headline.main: Egypt: Court Blocks Extradition of Ex-Qaddafi Aide to Libya
headline.print_headline: Egypt: Court Rules Against Extradition Of Former Qaddafi Aide to Libya
